{
  "stem": "21437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So if this sounds somehow-- for self preservation, I don't know what it is in a human being's mind that you can sometimes lock out something or, you know, dispose of something and retain other parts of it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before we went over that Russian border, which was Brzesc-- something comes to mind-- Brzesc nad Bugiem.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brzesc-- B-R-Z-- with those two-- E-S-C-- nad, which would be N-A-D, Bugiem, which would be B-U-G-E-M.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- yes, it was a city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- there was something like a stream, you know, like water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were, on the way before that, we stayed-- I remember must have been Rosh Hashanah, must have been between Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I remember that they took something like a chook.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, that was then-- that was a ritual that Yom Kippur, you know, they got around your head sort of for the chook, to have a good year, for you to have blessings.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whatever was supposed to await you, the chook, that was like a-- they were like three times over your head.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a blessing said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that must have been Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chicken, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember the legs and all, you know, was over my head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was petrified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as it was a dead chicken, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then I was very feverish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had something like a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], which was called [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember even where the bed was positioned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I was tossing and it was a huge bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must have been a very elegant home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we must have been there between Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur, something like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
